    "offline-message-com-apple-Mail-help" : {
      "navigation" : "false",
      "content" : "<div id='offline-message-com-apple-Mail-help' class='apd-topic'><div class='subjectids'><a name='offline-message-com-apple-Mail-help'><\/a><\/div><h1 class='title topictitle1'>所选主题当前不可用<\/h1><div class='body conbody'><p class='p'>请确定您的电脑已接入互联网。若要获得接入互联网的帮助，请选取苹果菜单 >“系统偏好设置”，点按“网络”，然后点按“向导”。<\/p><p class='p'>如果您的电脑已接入互联网，但是内容仍未显示，请稍后再试一次。<\/p><\/div><\/div>",
