    "cpmlwn" : {
      "navigation" : "false",
      "content" : "<div id='cpmlwn' class='apd-topic'><div class='subjectids'><a name='cpmlwn'><\/a><a name='almail38576'><\/a><a name='almail38577'><\/a><\/div><h1 class='title topictitle1'><img class='image category-art' src='..\/media\/xicnml.png' height='32' width='32'>Mail 的新功能<\/h1><div class='body taskbody'><div class='section context'><p class='p'>OS X Mountain Lion 中的 Mail 提供多种卓越的新功能，使得发送、接收和查看邮件更加简便。<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class='topic task nested1' id='cpmlwn-a'><a name='cpmlwn-a'><!-- --><\/a><h2 class='title topictitle2'>VIP<\/h2><div class='body taskbody'><div class='section context'><p class='p'>通过将非常重要的联系人设为 VIP，来跟踪他们发给您的邮件。您的 VIP 可通过您从他们接收到的邮件中的名称旁边的星号来识别。Mail 会为每个 VIP 添加一个邮箱到“个人收藏”栏，以便轻松获取他们的邮件。<\/p><p class='p'><a class='xref unresolved-reference' href='#mail40589'>让发件人成为 VIP<\/a><\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class='topic task nested1' id='cpmlwn-c'><a name='cpmlwn-c'><!-- --><\/a><h2 class='title topictitle2'>新邮件的通知<\/h2><div class='body taskbody'><div class='section context'><p class='p'>您可以在 Mail 偏好设置中设定选项以基于收件箱或发件人显示通知。<\/p><p class='p'><a class='xref unresolved-reference' href='#mail40585'>自定邮件通知的显示时间<\/a><\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class='topic task nested1' id='cpmlwn-e'><a name='cpmlwn-e'><!-- --><\/a><h2 class='title topictitle2'>以不同格式共享网页<\/h2><div class='body taskbody'><div class='section context'><p class='p'>当您从 Safari 共享网页时，您可以选取发送它的格式。例如，您可以将它作为链接或 PDF 来发送。<\/p><p class='p'><a class='xref unresolved-reference' href='#mail40723'>从 Safari 发送共享的网页<\/a><\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class='related-links'><div class='linklist linklist'><strong>相关主题<\/strong><br><div><a class='link unresolved-reference' href='#mail35803'>针对您的所有帐户发送和接收邮件<\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>",
